00:22:08.470 --> 00:22:10.130
Minsan ako ay nag-iisa at walang magawa,

00:22:11.990 --> 00:22:14.510
hindi ko alam kung saan sa ilang
ako mamamatay.

00:22:14.510 --> 00:22:15.440
Hindi ko inaasahan

00:22:17.270 --> 00:22:18.510
